content.query:
SELECT
    top (100)
[ESPECIALIDADE_UNIV]  COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gskoutputfiles/Email & KPI Visitacao/dimensao_audit_end.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) WITH (
 [ESPECIALIDADE_UNIV]	NVARCHAR(1000)
    ) AS ROW
